  <brief_title>Immunogenicity of Hepatitis B Vaccination Among Drug Users</brief_title>
  <official_title>Immunogenicity and Safety of High-dose Hepatitis B Vaccine Among Drug Users: a Randomized, Controlled Trial</official_title>
